        WELCOME_TO_OUR_HUMBLE_SHOP                                              = 7558,  -- Welcome to our humble shop!
        HELLO_WELCOME_TO_THE_MARBLE_BRIDGE_EACH_DAY                             = 7559,  -- Hello. Welcome to the Marble Bridge. Each day we have a new entrance policy. So, enjoy talking with your peers.
        I_M_SORRY_BUT_IT_S_TIME_FOR                                             = 7560,  -- I'm sorry, but it's time for you to go. Please come again!
        HUH_A_PETITION_TO_SAVE_THE_CLOCK_TOWER                                  = 7561,  -- Huh? A petition to save the clock tower? Where do I sign? So this is why Galmut looked so worried when he stopped by a while ago.
        THAT_GALMUT_HE_S_ALWAYS_PESTERING_US_TO                                 = 7562,  -- That Galmut... He's always pestering us to have a clock workers' day. I tell him nobody would come except for him and Mr. Narihira.
        TODAY_THE_MARBLE_BRIDGE_WELCOMES_ALL                                    = 7563,  -- ***Today the Marble Bridge welcomes all [San d'Orians/Bastokers/Windurstians/warriors/monks/white mages/black mages/red mages/thieves/paladins/dark knights/beastmasters/bards/rangers/samurais/ninjas/dragoons/summoners/blue mages/corsairs/puppetmasters/dancers/scholars/geomancers/rune fencers/Humes/Elvaan/Tarutaru/Mithra/Galka/gentlemen/ladies]!***
        COULD_I_ASK_YOU_A_FAVOR                                                 = 7564,  -- %, could I ask you a favor?
        YOU_KNOW_THAT_OUR_MOTTO_IS_EVERY_DAY                                    = 7565,  -- You know that our motto is every day is a special day, right? Well, lately I've been hearing lots of rumors about how confusing our entrance policies are.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_THINK_NO_PROBLEMS_AT_ALL                                    = 7566,  -- What do you think? No problems at all. They are pretty confusing...
        HAH_YOU_DON_T_HAVE_TO_BE_NICE                                           = 7567,  -- Hah, you don't have to be nice. I know what you're really thinking.
        HMMM_SO_YOU_THINK_SO_TOO_WELL_THEN                                      = 7568,  -- Hmmm... So you think so too... Well, then I guess that it's time to do something!
        AND_THAT_S_WHY_I_VE_COME_UP                                             = 7569,  -- And that's why I've come up with this plan. I've made up a batch of these special % that will let you know if today's your special day the moment you enter Upper Jeuno.
        AH_HA_I_KNEW_YOU_D_BE_BACK                                              = 7570,  -- Ah ha! I knew you'd be back! Can't live without %, can you?
        HOW_MUCH_NO_I_WOULDN_T_THINK_OF                                         = 7571,  -- How much? No! I wouldn't think of charging one of my best customers for something like this!
        WHAT_DO_YOU_SAY_I_LL_TAKE_ONE                                           = 7572,  -- What do you say? I'll take one! Thanks, but no thanks.
        WONDERFUL_REMEMBER_IF_YOU_THINK_THAT_YOU_NO                             = 7573,  -- Wonderful! Remember, if you think that you no longer need the coaster, just come back and I'll take it off your hands.
        OH_WELL_IF_YOU_EVER_CHANGE_YOUR_MIND                                    = 7574,  -- Oh... Well, if you ever change your mind, just come back any time. I've made up hundreds of these things!
        HOW_DO_YOU_LIKE_THE_PRETTY_USEFUL_HUH                                   = 7575,  -- How do you like the %? Pretty useful, huh?
        WHAT_DO_YOU_THINK_I_WANT_TO_RETURN                                      = 7576,  -- What do you think? I want to return the coaster. I can't live without my coaster!
        YOU_WANT_TO_RETURN_IT_WELL_I_CAN                                        = 7577,  -- You want to return it!? Well, I can't force you to carry it around... You know what they say, The customer is always right. But if you ever need another one, you know where to come!
        HEH_HEH_I_KNEW_YOU_D_SAY_THAT                                           = 7578,  -- Heh heh! I knew you'd say that!
        YOU_RETURN_THE                                                          = 7579,  -- You return the %.
        GREETINGS_WE_DEAL_IN_ALL_SORTS_OF_ARMOR                                 = 7580,  -- Greetings! We deal in all sorts of armor. They say the best defense is a good offense, but it never hurts to play it safe.
        I_KNOW_IT_SOUNDS_OBVIOUS_BUT_A_GOOD                                     = 7581,  -- I know it sounds obvious, but a good suit of armor can save your life.
        HELLO_WE_VE_GOT_EVERYTHING_FROM_DOUBLE_EDGED                            = 7582,  -- Hello! We've got everything from double-edged swords to big, two-handed axes.
        HELLO_HOW_ABOUT_SOME_PRODUCE_FROM_ARAGONEU                              = 7583,  -- Hello. How about some produce from Aragoneu?
        I_VE_GOT_PRODUCE_FROM_RONFAURE                                          = 7584,  -- I've got produce from Ronfaure!
        HELLO_GUSTABERG_PRODUCE_FOR_SALE                                        = 7585,  -- Hello. Gustaberg produce for sale!
        FRESH_PRODUCE_FROM_FAUREGANDI                                           = 7586,  -- Fresh produce from Fauregandi!
        LOOKING_FOR_DERFLAND_PRODUCE                                            = 7587,  -- Looking for Derfland produce?
        HOW_ABOUT_SOME_FRESH_GOODS_FROM_NORVALLEN                               = 7588,  -- How about some fresh goods from Norvallen?
        LONG_AGO_THE_GODDESS_ALTANA_TOOK_PITY_ON                                = 7589,  -- Long ago, the Goddess Altana took pity on the barren world of Vana'diel and shed five tears. Our ancestors sprouted from each one.
        BUT_THE_GOD_PROMATHIA_SAW_THIS_AND_CONDEMNED                            = 7590,  -- But the god Promathia saw this, and condemned her work. He cursed all her people to eternal conflict among each other.
        ALTANA_WOULD_NOT_BE_PLEASED_TO_SEE_US                                   = 7591,  -- Altana would not be pleased to see us now, squabbling over our petty causes. Please, at least while you are here, shun conflict and pray for peace.
        THE_CANDLES_MADE_HERE_ARE_BLESSED_WITH_A                                = 7592,  -- The candles made here are blessed with a special prayer: May this holy light cleanse the world of shadow.
        SAY_YOU_HERE_FOR_BUSINESS_THIS_TOWN_S                                   = 7593,  -- Say, you here for business? This town's a mecca for merchants, you know, since all roads lead to Jeuno!
        PEOPLE_COME_FULL_OF_HOPE_WITH_GREAT_DREAMS                              = 7594,  -- People come full of hope, with great dreams and plans for the future. Our free city is a melting pot for all mankind!
        BUT_NOT_EVERYBODY_SOME_JUST_PICK_UP_AND                                 = 7595,  -- But not everybody. Some just pick up and head for home. Where there is light, there is shadow. That's Jeuno!
        YOU_KNOW_WOLFGANG_HAS_CHANGED_SO_MUCH_EVER                              = 7596,  -- You know, Wolfgang has changed so much ever since he became captain of the guard. It's like he's always wearing a mask. He never smiles anymore.
        HE_EVEN_GIVES_HIS_OLD_PAL_MONBERAUX_THE                                 = 7597,  -- He even gives his old pal Monberaux the cold shoulder. Just who does he think he is!
        SOMEWHERE_OUT_THERE_MY_NEMESIS_AWAITS_HER_POWER                         = 7598,  -- Somewhere out there, my nemesis awaits... Her power is so great, I tremble just mentioning her.
        YES_ONLY_THE_STURDIEST_MAIL_COULD_SAVE_ME                               = 7599,  -- Yes, only the sturdiest mail could save me from her terrible strikes! Armor should always be carefully chosen!
        HEY_HAVE_YOU_SEEN_MY_GOOD_FOR_NOTHING                                   = 7600,  -- Hey, have you seen my good-for-nothing husband anywhere? I know he's cheating on me!
        ONCE_I_GET_MY_HANDS_ON_HIM_I                                            = 7601,  -- Once I get my hands on him I'll mash him into a bloody pulp! Now, which weapon would inflict the most pain... We must choose our weapons carefully!
        GLORY_BE_TO_ALTANA_EVER_DOES_SHE_WATCH                                  = 7602,  -- Glory be to Altana! Ever does she watch over her flock.
        IF_YOU_FIND_YOURSELF_IN_NEED_PRAY_TO                                    = 7603,  -- If you find yourself in need, pray to her. Only through her divine light can we see the truth.
        YOU_KNOW_THIS_PUB_S_GOT_DIFFERENT_REQUIREMENTS                          = 7604,  -- You know, this pub's got different requirements to get in every day. Like on Tarutaru Day, only Tarutaru can get intaru!
        SO_WHENEVER_YOU_RE_THERE_YOU_CAN_TALK                                   = 7605,  -- So whenever you're there, you can talk with your peers... You know? I always have a blast, so try it outaru!
        I_VE_NEVER_LOST_A_FIGHT_HERE_THIS                                       = 7606,  -- I've never lost a fight here. This town is full of wimps!
        HOW_DARE_THAT_PANTA_SEND_ME_A_CHALLENGE                                 = 7607,  -- How dare that Panta send me a challenge! I bet he's still fuming over that beating I gave him.
        I_WONDER_WHAT_PANTA_S_GONNA_BRING_THIS                                  = 7608,  -- I wonder what Panta's gonna bring this time. Eh, won't help that pipsqueak anyway.
        HAH_THAT_PANTA_S_STILL_AT_IT_WELL                                       = 7609,  -- Hah! That Panta's still at it.. Well, I don't care. He'll never beat me with this kind of stuff!
        OH_YEAH_THE_GOBLINS_WERE_CARRYING_PANTA_S                               = 7610,  -- Oh, yeah. The Goblins were carrying Panta's Cardian to the doctor's. I wonder what's going on...
        PANTA_NEVER_CRIES_AFTER_HE_LOSES_A_FIGHT                                = 7611,  -- Panta never cries after he loses a fight, but he was bawling after he left the doctor's. Maybe he had a cavity?
