        HOWEVER_IF_YOU_STILL_WISH_TO_TAKE_PART                                  = 8559,  -- However, if you still wish to take part in Ballista, participation in matches held within Diorama Abdhaljs-Ghelsba is open to all citizens of Vana'diel.
