        THOUGH_TENDER_OF_AGE_YOUR_TALENT_HAD_ALREADY                            = 12074,  -- Though tender of age, your talent had already bloomed beyond compare. Never before had such a young dancer been selected lead in your mother's production--even I knew this...
        BUT_I_HAD_NO_RIGHT_TO_PLUCK_YOU                                         = 12075,  -- But I had no right to pluck you away from where you belonged.
        YOU_DESERVED_SO_MUCH_MORE_THAN_I_COULD                                  = 12076,  -- You deserved so much more than I could have ever offered in my troupe.
        NO_CIRCUS_TENT_COULD_EVER_BE_LARGE_ENOUGH                               = 12077,  -- No circus tent could ever be large enough for you to grow and fulfill your potential, Laila...
        SO_YE_REJECTED_ME_NOT_BECAUSE_YE_DIDN                                   = 12078,  -- So...ye rejected me not because ye didn't think I was good enough?
        THE_ANSWER_IS_CLEAR_LAILA_YOU_ARE_EVERYTHING                            = 12079,  -- The answer is clear, Laila. You are everything a dancer could ever wish to be.
        I_REGRET_NOT_HAVING_EXPLAINED_MY_DECISION_MORE                          = 12080,  -- I regret not having explained my decision more clearly when I turned you down.
        EVEN_IF_YE_DID_I_DON_T_THINK                                            = 12081,  -- Even if ye did, I don't think I would've understood...
        I_SO_WANTED_T_JOIN_TROUPE_VALERIANO_I                                   = 12082,  -- I so wanted t'join Troupe Valeriano, I lost sight o' all those who cared about me most...
        I_WAS_AM_JUST_A_STUPID_GIRL                                             = 12083,  -- I was--am--just a stupid girl...
        YOU_NEED_NOT_BE_ASHAMED                                                 = 12084,  -- You need not be ashamed.
        JUST_LOOK_AT_THE_WONDERFUL_DANCE_TROUPE_THAT                            = 12085,  -- Just look at the wonderful dance troupe that you have created! Cast your eyes upon the scores of fans who love you!
        V_VALERIANO_2                                                           = 12086,  -- V-Valeriano...
        LAILA_WILL_YOU_DO_ME_THE_GREAT_HONOR                                    = 12087,  -- Laila... Will you do me the great honor of dancing for me? Just like that time so many years ago?
        AYE                                                                     = 12088,  -- Aye!
        I_HAVE_NEVER_ENJOYED_PERFORMING_AS_I_DID                                = 12089,  -- I have never enjoyed performing as I did today. I very much look forward to our next collaboration.
        ALRIGHT_EVERYONE_IT_S_TIME_TO_GO                                        = 12090,  -- Alright everyone, it's time to go.
        HM                                                                      = 12091,  -- Hm?
        THAT_PEBBLE                                                             = 12092,  -- That pebble...
        MY_S_TWIN_SO_YOU_HAD_IT_WITH                                            = 12093,  -- My %'s twin... So you had it with you all this time.
        THEY_FINALLY_FOUND_EACH_OTHER_AGAIN                                     = 12094,  -- They finally found each other again...
        I_M_GOIN_T_START_OVER_JUST_LIKE                                         = 12095,  -- I'm goin' t'start over. Just like the day I found this pebble by the lake.
        I_TRUST_IT_WILL_NOT_TAKE_ANOTHER_TWENTY                                 = 12096,  -- I trust it will not take another twenty years before I next see you dance. All the best, Laila.
        WERE_MY_EYES_JUST_PLAYING_TRRRICKS_ON_ME                                = 12097,  -- Were my eyes just playing trrricks on me? Could it actually be...true?
        WHAT_AM_I_TALKING_ABOUT                                                 = 12098,  -- What am I talking about?
        YOU_SEE_THERE_IS_A_LEGEND_THAT_SAYS                                     = 12099,  -- You see, there is a legend that says that the most talented and grrraceful of dancers are visited by the Divinity of Dance.
        BUT_I_NEVER_ACTUALLY_BELIEVED_IT_UNTIL_THIS                             = 12100,  -- But I never actually believed it until this day... Just now when Laila was dancing, I could have sworn...
        BUT_BEFORRRE_I_FORGET_LAILA_WAS_WANTING_TO                              = 12101,  -- But beforrre I forget, Laila was wanting to give something to you, %. Why don't you go and speak with her?
        THAT_WAS_A_HELLUVA_DEBUT_PERFORMANCE_YE_NEVER                           = 12102,  -- That was a helluva debut performance, %. Ye never cease t'impress me.
        NOTHIN_RINGS_TRUER_THAN_PRACTICE_MAKES_PERFECT_HERE                     = 12103,  -- Nothin' rings truer than practice makes perfect. Here, this is fer all yer hard work.
        I_VE_BEEN_SUCH_A_FOOL_ALL_THESE                                         = 12104,  -- I've been such a fool all these years, usin' dance just t'try to patch up me broken ego.
        IT_S_KINDA_EMBARRASSIN_TO_ADMIT_BUT_I                                   = 12105,  -- It's kinda embarrassin' to admit, but I haven't enjoyed dancin' like that fer ages.
        HOW_I_D_LOVE_T_DANCE_BESIDE_VALERIANO                                   = 12106,  -- How I'd love t'dance beside Valeriano again...
        HERE_TAKE_THIS_YE_DESERVE_IT_FER_ALL                                    = 12107,  -- Here, take this. Ye deserve it fer all yer hard work.
        DANCE_CAN_BE_ILLUSIVE_AT_TIMES_THE_HARDER                               = 12108,  -- Dance can be illusive at times--the harder ye seek, the more ye lose sight o' it...
        WHEN_THAT_HAPPENS_JUST_CLEAR_ALL_UNNECESSARY_THOUGHTS                   = 12109,  -- When that happens, just clear all unnecessary thoughts from ye mind an' ev'rythin' will be alright.
        I_WILL_STRRRIVE_TO_BECOME_A_GREAT_DANCER                                = 12110,  -- I will strrrive to become a great dancer like Laila.
        GOLLY_I_CAN_T_REMEMBER_THE_LAST_TIME                                    = 12111,  -- Golly! I can't remember the last time I enjoyed myself so much!
        YOU_RE_SO_PRETTY_I_WANNA_BE_A                                           = 12112,  -- You're so pretty! I wanna be a dancer like you someday!
        I_REMEMBER_A_TIME_DURING_THE_CRYSTAL_WAR                                = 12113,  -- I remember a time during the Crystal War when I found myself surrounded by the enemy in battle. I had given up all hope when Field Musician dancers came to my rescue.
        WITH_LITTLE_MORE_THAN_A_GRACEFUL_WAVE_OF                                = 12114,  -- With little more than a graceful wave of their arms, my wounds were healed and pains soothed. It felt as though the Goddess herself had descended from her celestial realm...
        THE_PERFORMANCE_WAS_TOUCHING_BEYOND_WORDS_I_HAVE                        = 12115,  -- The performance was touching beyond words. I have not a shred of doubt in my heart that the Divinity of Dance exists...
        PRACTICIN_HARD_AS_USUAL                                                 = 12116,  -- Practicin' hard as usual, %?
        I_VE_BEEN_MEANIN_TO_ASK_YE_HAVE                                         = 12117,  -- I've been meanin' to ask ye, have ye ever heard of %?
        THEY_RE_MARKS_THAT_THE_DIVINITY_O_DANCE                                 = 12118,  -- They're marks that the Divinity o' Dance bestows t'dancers who are deemed worthy.
        YE_VE_TRAVELED_THROUGH_MANY_A_LAND_DURIN                                = 12119,  -- Ye've traveled through many a land durin' yer trainin' t'become a dancer.
        IF_YE_RETRACE_YER_STEPS_THE_DIVINITY_O                                  = 12120,  -- If ye retrace yer steps, the Divinity o' Dance may appear before ye an' present ye with %.
        IF_THAT_EVER_HAPPENS_BRING_THE_BACK_HERE                                = 12121,  -- If that ever happens, bring the % back here an' show me.
        GOT_YERSELF_YE_SAY_GIVE_US_A_GANDER                                     = 12122,  -- Got yerself %, ye say? Give us a gander.
        THERE_S_NO_MISTAKIN_THIS_IS_THE_REAL                                    = 12123,  -- There's no mistakin', this is the real McCoy...
        THIS_MEANS_THE_DIVINITY_O_DANCE_HAS_DEEMED                              = 12124,  -- This means the Divinity o' Dance has deemed ye worthy. Ye've earned the right t'undertake the test t'become Diva o' the Dance Troupe.
        IT_S_A_TITLE_GIVEN_T_DANCERS_WHO                                        = 12125,  -- It's a title given t'dancers who are blessed by the Divinity o' Dance. The catch is, there can be no more than one such dancer in a troupe.
        YE_CAN_NOW_CHALLENGE_T_BECOME_TROUPE_BRILIOTH                           = 12126,  -- Ye can now challenge t'become Troupe Brilioth's diva.
        WHO_S_GONNA_TEST_YE_WHY_THAT_LL                                         = 12127,  -- Who's gonna test ye? Why, that'll be yers truly, of course. I never imagined this day would come.
        IN_OUR_MARTIAL_STYLE_THERE_S_NO_BETTER                                  = 12128,  -- In our martial style, there's no better way t'test one's ability than t'go head-to-head. But don't ye think I'll be holdin' back, %.
        WE_LL_DUKE_IT_OUT_AT_QU_BIA                                             = 12129,  -- We'll duke it out at Qu'Bia Arena. Ye ready to go?
        GO_TO_QU_BIA_ARENA_READY_WHEN_YOU                                       = 12130,  -- Go to Qu'Bia Arena? Ready when you are! I need time to prepare...
        IS_THAT_SO_THEN_COME_BACK_HERE_AFTER                                    = 12131,  -- Is that so. Then come back here after ye've finished whatever ye have t'do.
        GOOD_WHEN_YE_ARRIVE_USE_YER_T_ENTER                                     = 12132,  -- Good. When ye arrive, use yer % t'enter the arena.
        YOUR_IS_TORN                                                            = 12133,  -- Your % is torn...
        YER_DESTINY_IS_T_SEEK_OUT_BIGGER_STAGES                                 = 12134,  -- Yer destiny is t'seek out bigger stages until ye one day become diva to the whole o' Vana'diel.
        PRRROMISE_ME_YOU_LL_COME_BACK_TO_DANCE                                  = 12135,  -- Prrromise me you'll come back to dance with us again, %.
        DIVA_OF_THE_DANCE_TROUPE_IT_SOUNDS_SO                                   = 12136,  -- Diva of the Dance Troupe... It sounds so dreamy... <Sigh>
        OH_HEY_THERE_I_WAS_WONDERING_WHERE_YOU                                  = 12137,  -- Oh hey there, %. I was wondering where you were.
        I_VE_BEEN_MEANING_TO_HAVE_A_HEART                                       = 12138,  -- I've been meaning to have a heart-to-heart with you for some time now. Don't take this the wrong way, but...have you ever considered getting a tailor-made dancer outfit? Hmmm?
        AS_PROFESSIONALS_WE_HAVE_TO_TAKE_EXTRA_CARE                             = 12139,  -- As professionals, we have to take extra care with our appearance, you know. And it just so happens that there's this tailor I know you'd just love!
        HIS_NAME_IS_MATTHIAS_THE_GARMENTS_HE_MAKES                              = 12140,  -- His name is Matthias. The garments he makes at his shop in Bastok Markets are simply sublime!
        WE_VE_ALL_HAD_OUR_OUTFITS_MADE_UP                                       = 12141,  -- We've all had our outfits made up by Matthias, even the % Laila's wearing. Just gorgeous, aren't they?
        YOU_SHOULD_DEFINITELY_HAVE_MATTHIAS_MAKE_YOU_AN                         = 12142,  -- You should definitely have Matthias make you an outfit, too. I promise you won't regret it!
        YOU_SHOULD_DEFINITELY_HAVE_HIM_MAKE_YOU_AN                              = 12143,  -- You should definitely have him make you an outfit, too. I promise you won't regret it!
        WELL_WELL_AREN_T_WE_LOOKING_DASHING_GORGEOUS                            = 12144,  -- Well, well, aren't we looking dashing/gorgeous] today? I see you've been a good boy/girl] and went to see Matthias, just like I recommended!
        BUT_OH_WOW_YOUR_DANCER_ATTIRE_I_IT                                      = 12145,  -- But, oh wow... Your dancer attire... I-it's lovelier than I had expected. It's as though...the Divinity of Dance is among us...
        YOU_A_FAN_OF_THE_DANCE_AS_WELL                                          = 12146,  -- You a fan of the dance as well, then?
        DON_T_GET_ME_WRONG_THE_DANCE_SHOWS                                      = 12147,  -- Don't get me wrong, the dance shows that are put on nowadays are all well and good. But they're nothing compared to the shows of old, back in the days when dance was in its prime!
        YOU_EVER_HEAR_OF_TROUPE_MAYAKOV_THEY_WERE                               = 12148,  -- You ever hear of Troupe Mayakov? They were one of the more popular dance troupes making the rounds about the time of the Crystal War.
        THEY_HAD_A_YOUNG_GIRL_AMONGST_THEM_ABSOLUTELY                           = 12149,  -- They had a young girl amongst them. Absolutely beautiful thing. The Moonshade Butterfly, they called her. They are still talking in San d'Oria today about the solo performance she gave in Lion Square all those years ago.
        I_WAS_LUCKY_ENOUGH_TO_GET_HOLD_OF                                       = 12150,  -- I was lucky enough to get hold of a ticket for that show. Got all the way to the tavern before my wife managed to track me down and drag me back home.
        SIGH_THAT_S_ONE_REGRET_THAT_LL_STAY                                     = 12151,  -- <Sigh>... That's one regret that'll stay with me the rest of my days.
        EVEN_NOW_I_STILL_CARRY_THE_TICKET_WITH                                  = 12152,  -- Even now I still carry the ticket with me. Just as a reminder of how close I once came to seeing perfection on the stage.
        SEE_HAVE_A_LOOK_IT_S_GOTTEN_QUITE                                       = 12153,  -- See, have a look. It's gotten quite beaten up over the years, as can be expected. I don't suppose there's much use in hanging on to it anymore, though.
