        WELL_NOW_IT_SEEMS_HAS_TAKEN_TO_THESE_8                                  = 13103,  -- Well now, it seems [Durib/Dzapiwa/Jugowa/Mugido/Voldai/Wagwei/Zayag/Zoldof] has taken to these trrrials like a Goblin gambler to beastcoins. Here's your missive, by the way.
        AND_DON_T_BOTHER_ASKING_ABOUT_MY_FAILING                                = 13104,  -- And don't bother asking about my failing business. It'll just rrrub me the wrong way. Keep your mind on the trial at hand, not my stupid plight.
        TO_TELL_THE_TRRRUTH_I_WANTED_TO_PUT                                     = 13105,  -- To tell the trrruth, I wanted to put your new skills to good use. Sadly, this dumb world isn't so forrrgiving. All we need is for one lousy job to come our way!
        IT_FIGURES_IT_S_ALWAYS_THE_ILL_WINDS                                    = 13106,  -- It figures... It's always the ill winds and never the gentle breezes that blow our way.
        THIS_SIMPLY_ISN_T_FAIR_I_CANNOT_ABIDE                                   = 13107,  -- This simply isn't fair! I cannot abide the fact that my failures are utterly ruining you, Luto!
