        I_M_NOT_HALF_BAD_I_WAGER_I                                              = 13140,  -- I'm not half bad. I wager I could go one-on-one with the Shadow Lord and barely even break a sweat.
        I_FEEL_QUITE_EMPOWERED_THANK_YOU_ALL_MY                                 = 13141,  -- I feel quite empowered, thank you. All my senses seem heightened to the point where, for a fleeting moment, I almost questioned my mortality.
        WHAT_CAN_I_SAY_I_M_READY_TO                                             = 13142,  -- What can I say? I'm ready to sink my teeth deep into the next job and tear off a chunk of absolute victory!
        I_FEEL_GOOD_ENOUGH_TO_ASK_YOU_OUT                                       = 13143,  -- I feel good enough to ask you out to dinner with me next week. Stay that thought! I'm not sure you're ready for me yet, my dear.
