        THIS_FEELING_IS_THE_BEST_IT_S_LIKE                                      = 13147,  -- This feeling is the best! It's like I huffed and puffed and blew down a wall that was blocking me! Now, what would you call that? A boundary bust, maybe?
        WHAT_A_SPECTACULAR_SENSATION_I_CAN_FEEL_AN                              = 13148,  -- What a spectacular sensation. I can feel an unbelievable power welling up from the very depths of my being, surging through my limbs...
