        YES_ANOTHER_CHANCE_FOR_ME_TO_KICK_SOME                                  = 13200,  -- Yes! Another chance for me to kick some serious monster tuchus! Still, when I think of how we haven't gotten any work in forever...I...I...waaahhh!
        IT_S_TIME_ONCE_AGAIN_FOR_A_TRIAL                                        = 13201,  -- It's time once again for a trial in tandem, is it? Of course, I'm completely fine with undertaking this task so crucial to my own development, but--if I may--it does seem a tad suspicious that we never actually receive any job offers.
        YOU_MEAN_WE_RE_GOING_OFF_ON_ANOTHER                                     = 13202,  -- You mean we're going off on another tangemawhatsit? Then I have to dig down deep and find my inner strength so we can bop those baddies and get some real work!
