        ANOTHER_ONE_OF_THESE_CURSED_TRIALS_AS_MUCH                              = 13204,  -- Another one of these cursed trials!? As much as the sight of scattered monster entrails beneath my bootheel excites me, I can't subsist on excitement alone! What about some real work!?
        HEH_HEH_HEH_YOU_MAY_THINK_THIS_IS                                       = 13205,  -- Heh heh heh. You may think this is just another trial in tandem, but you'd be wrrrong. Your ever-resourceful boss has sifted through Jeuno's litterbox of a marketplace and finally come up with a gem of a job! Ha, whoever said, Curiosity killed the cat was dumb as a dagon!
