        YEEEAAAH_IT_S_TIME_TO_GO_A_SMASHIN                                      = 13209,  -- Yeeeaaah! It's time to go a-smashin' and a-bashin' and a-crashin' in the name of good, old-fashioned work! Let's grab this opportunity by the horns and shake it 'til they break off! It's Ru'Lude or bust, %!
        WELL_ANOTHER_JOB_HAD_TO_COME_EVENTUALLY_IT                              = 13210,  -- Well, another job had to come eventually. It might as well be now. Come on, %--to the gardens.
        WHAT_A_WELCOME_DEVELOPMENT_LUTO_I_PROMISE_NOT                           = 13211,  -- What a welcome development, Luto. I promise not to disappoint you in this entrepreneurial venture. I assume you do not want to disappoint her either, %? Then let us depart for Ru'Lude.
        I_KNEW_YOU_D_PULL_THROUGH_FOR_US                                        = 13212,  -- I knew you'd pull through for us, Luto! Yay! We finally did it! A chocobo in the stable is worth two in the bush, so let's ride on over to Ru'Lude before our meal ticket leaves town, %!
        THIS_IS_JUST_THE_CHANCE_I_NEED_TO                                       = 13213,  -- This is just the chance I need to prove how dashing and daring I can be. Be forewarned, Luto, lest you fall so hard for me that you can't get back up. %. You, me, Ru'Lude. Now.
        OH_MY_WHAT_IMPECCABLE_TIMING_AND_HERE_I                                 = 13214,  -- Oh my, what impeccable timing! And here I was just thinking how nice it would be if we could see some work drift our way. It must be fate! Come now, %, it's off to Ru'Lude for us.
