        YET_MOVING_TOO_HASTILY_HAS_CAUSED_THE_DOWNFALL                          = 14023,  -- Yet moving too hastily has caused the downfall of many, so I would ask for your aid once more.
        THE_FIRST_ISSUE_IS_DEALING_WITH_THE_DEFECTORS                           = 14024,  -- The first issue is dealing with the defectors amongst the beastmen who have joined forces with Chaos.
        UNFORTUNATELY_THEIR_CONTINGENT_IS_PRESENT_NOT_ONLY_IN                   = 14025,  -- Unfortunately, their contingent is present not only in the Middle Lands, but Aht Urhgan and the Far East as well.
        WITH_THE_ENEMY_SPREAD_OUT_ACROSS_THE_WORLD                              = 14026,  -- With the enemy spread out across the world, I have had to dispatch some of my most loyal retainers to the far reaches of the globe.
        WHILE_THEY_ARE_DEALING_WITH_THE_THREAT_ABOVE                            = 14027,  -- While they are dealing with the threat above, you will deal with Garazu-Horeizu at the gate between this world and the next.
        OF_COURSE_THIS_WILL_ALLOW_THE_GATE_TO                                   = 14028,  -- Of course, this will allow the gate to be opened.
        I_WILL_TAKE_UP_THE_REAR_GUARD_SO                                        = 14029,  -- I will take up the rear guard, so you have not to fear.
        AH_BUT_PERHAPS_YOU_ARE_CONCERNED_THAT_MY                                = 14030,  -- Ah, but perhaps you are concerned that my protection alone may prove insufficient.
        ARE_YOU_CONCERNED_OF_COURSE_OF_COURSE_NOT                               = 14031,  -- Are you concerned? Of course! Of course not!
