        BUT_I_DO_ADMIRE_YOUR_GUMPTION                                           = 14067,  -- But I do admire your gumption.
        I_AM_NOT_AN_UNREASONABLE_MAN_IF_YOU                                     = 14068,  -- I am not an unreasonable man. If you are able to best them again if and when they should appear in our plane, then who am I to deny you an extra prize?
